a proper deep lifting position.</p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1658550776190" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1658550776190"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>So, before purchasing, make sure your ankle mobility is good enough to utilize the shoe.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662731768500" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662731768500" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Nike-Blazer-Vintage-White-Black/dp/B07QSYZL1P/?tag=are-nike-blazers-good-for-lifting-20" target="_blank"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/c63d388a-d0fd-4d61-b4c9-80b2ded6bbc5/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Nike%20Men_s%20Basketball%20Shoe.png" alt="Nike Shoes Blazer " class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1388" height="1062" data-width="40%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1388" natural-height="1062"></a></div></div><div data-label="Button" data-key="button" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662731801349" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-gpicon-button" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662731801349"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-stretch-lg="0"><a class="button btn gf_button gf_gs-button-element gf_gs-button---large" href="https://www.amazon.com/Nike-Blazer-Vintage-White-Black/dp/B07QSYZL1P/?tag=are-nike-blazers-good-for-lifting-20" target="_blank" data-scroll-speed="2000" data-exc=""><span>Check Latest price</span></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1657333544672" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1657333544672"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">FAQ</h2></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1656945266692" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1656945266692"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Are Nike Blazers Good for Deadlifting?</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1656945244430" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1656945244430"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;">A <a href="https://www.bodybuilding.com/content/how-to-deadlift-layne-nortons-complete-guide.html" class="" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(30, 115, 190);">deadlift</a> is a full body exercise that starts at the feet as you get into a proper lifting position. What you really want to do is drive up from your heels, generating power that transfers through your body as you perform the lift. Having a flat heel of this is a good idea as it will allow you to generate power properly. So, a Nike Blazer is a good deadlifting shoe as it will aid your heel drive.</p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1658550894851" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1658550894851"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-p